58. inclusive make gate control
      Converts a quantum gate of n qubits to be n qubits and treat some qubits within the gate as control, and still act on these qubits. Operates element-wise across collections of gates and control qubit indices.
      Syntax: x = ctrli(Gate, Control Qubits)
      Allowed types for x & Gate: gate, matrix, block, circ, list, set, map, dict, struct.
      Allowed types for Control Qubit: qubit, cbit, qnum, qnump, cnum, qstr, qstrs, qstrc, qstre, cstr, cstrs, ctrc, cstre, matrix, block, circ, list, set, map, dict, gate, struct.
      Examples:
      a = H⊗H⊗H 
            [  1/(2√2)   1/(2√2)   1/(2√2)   1/(2√2)   1/(2√2)   1/(2√2)   1/(2√2)   1/(2√2) ]
            [  1/(2√2)  -1/(2√2)   1/(2√2)  -1/(2√2)   1/(2√2)  -1/(2√2)   1/(2√2)  -1/(2√2) ]
            [  1/(2√2)   1/(2√2)  -1/(2√2)  -1/(2√2)   1/(2√2)   1/(2√2)  -1/(2√2)  -1/(2√2) ]
            [  1/(2√2)  -1/(2√2)  -1/(2√2)   1/(2√2)   1/(2√2)  -1/(2√2)  -1/(2√2)   1/(2√2) ]
            [  1/(2√2)   1/(2√2)   1/(2√2)   1/(2√2)  -1/(2√2)  -1/(2√2)  -1/(2√2)  -1/(2√2) ]
            [  1/(2√2)  -1/(2√2)   1/(2√2)  -1/(2√2)  -1/(2√2)   1/(2√2)  -1/(2√2)   1/(2√2) ]
            [  1/(2√2)   1/(2√2)  -1/(2√2)  -1/(2√2)  -1/(2√2)  -1/(2√2)   1/(2√2)   1/(2√2) ]
            [  1/(2√2)  -1/(2√2)  -1/(2√2)   1/(2√2)  -1/(2√2)   1/(2√2)   1/(2√2)  -1/(2√2) ]

      x = ctrli(a,0) returns (|0⟩⟨0| ⊗ I₄) + (|1⟩⟨1| ⊗ I₄) · a
            [        1         0         0         0   1/(2√2)   1/(2√2)   1/(2√2)   1/(2√2) ]
            [        0         1         0         0   1/(2√2)  -1/(2√2)   1/(2√2)  -1/(2√2) ]
            [        0         0         1         0   1/(2√2)   1/(2√2)  -1/(2√2)  -1/(2√2) ]
            [        0         0         0         1   1/(2√2)  -1/(2√2)  -1/(2√2)   1/(2√2) ]
            [        0         0         0         0  -1/(2√2)  -1/(2√2)  -1/(2√2)  -1/(2√2) ]
            [        0         0         0         0  -1/(2√2)   1/(2√2)  -1/(2√2)   1/(2√2) ]
            [        0         0         0         0  -1/(2√2)  -1/(2√2)   1/(2√2)   1/(2√2) ]
            [        0         0         0         0  -1/(2√2)   1/(2√2)   1/(2√2)  -1/(2√2) ]

      x = ctrli(a,{0,2}) returns  (I₈ - |1⟩⟨1| ⊗ I₂ ⊗ |1⟩⟨1|) + a · (|1⟩⟨1| ⊗ I₂ ⊗ |1⟩⟨1|)
